---
title: Spicy Coconut Curry Pork Noodle Soup with Bok Choy, Napa Cabbage & Lemon
description: This coconut curry soup warms our hearts (and our palates!). Our chefs made tonights’ soup with ground pork, slurpable ramen noodles, fresh bok choy and cabbage, and all the craveable coconut curry and chili flavors. Curl up in your favorite spot, because you’re about to be warmed from head to toe with this delicious, spicy soup.
